name: Sin Kang TCM Clinic - Alexandra Retail Centre

reviews.text: I thoroughly enjoyed every session with Cui Yi Shi and Ying Ying. They are professional, friendly, and highly knowledgeable. Even the massage therapists are highly skilled. The outlet is bright, clean, and inviting, creating a welcoming atmosphere. After a couple of months with them, I’ve noticed a significant improvement in my overall health. While the pricing isn’t the lowest, the results and the warm, friendly environment make it well worth the investment.
Professional TCM treatment, my therapist Suki has helped me fix my many muscular and postural issues. Always look for her when I feel I need an adjustment. 10/10 would recommend!

Had my tuina this morning and was served by Miss Suki. Very experience therapist and she knew exactly where is your pain points and work on it. Strongly recommend her if you are looking for a good tuina therapist.
Amy was a skilled therapist. Has done a few sessions with her & got much better after every single one. Highly recommend

Sis. Suki i like the way she  do my massage .. She knows how to guide out the  pain out of your nerve . And  very sensible .Asking whether you feel comfortable or not..i can give her 8 out of 10 score..
